<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Premium Footwear Surat | Find Your Perfect Pair</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #1a1a1a;
            --accent: #e63946;
            --light: #f8f9fa;
        }
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0; color: var(--primary); background: var(--light); }
        
        /* Hero Section */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542291026-7eec264c27ff?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000');
            background-size: cover; background-position: center;
            height: 60vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            text-align: center; color: white; padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        .hero-content h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .hero-content p { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 30px; }

        /* CTA Button Styling */
        .cta-button {
            background-color: var(--accent);
            color: white; padding: 15px 35px;
            text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px; transition: 0.3s;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .cta-button:hover { background-color: #c12a36; transform: translateY(-2px); }

        /* Store Grid */
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 25px; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transition: 0.3s; }
        .card:hover { transform: scale(1.02); }
        .card h3 { margin-top: 0; color: var(--accent); }
        
        /* Footer/CTS */
        footer { background: var(--primary); color: white; text-align: center; padding: 40px 20px; margin-top: 50px; }
        .cts-links a { color: #adb5bd; margin: 0 15px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .cts-links a:hover { color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Step Into Style in Surat</h1>
        <p>Discover the latest collection of premium sneakers, formal shoes, and sports gear.</p>
        <a href="#stores" class="cta-button">EXPLORE TOP COLLECTIONS</a>
    </div>
</header>

<div class="container" id="stores">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">Featured Brands & Stores</h2>
    <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Campus Shoes</h3>
            <p>Running, Walking & Casual footwear for the active lifestyle.</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> VR Mall, Dumas Road</p>
            <a href="https://stores.campusshoes.com" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">View Store →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Metro Shoes</h3>
            <p>Quality footwear for men, women, and kids for every occasion.</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> Solaris Kode, VIP Road</p>
            <a href="https://stores.metroshoes.com" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">View Store →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Skechers</h3>
            <p>Leading the way in comfort technology and trendy athletic designs.</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> Ram Nagar, Katargam</p>
            <a href="https://www.skechers.in" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">Shop Online →</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Surat Footwear Guide. Your destination for style.</p>
    <div class="cts-links">
        <a href="#">Contact Us</a> | <a href="#">Store Locator</a> | <a href="#">Follow on Instagram</a>
    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
